267
00:26:15,707 --> 00:26:15,730
Together, we can take San Pedro.

268
00:26:15,840 --> 00:26:16,966
Yes, sir.

269
00:26:18,944 --> 00:26:20,036
Bull.

270
00:26:24,182 --> 00:26:25,946
Go to San Pedro now.

271
00:26:26,084 --> 00:26:29,850
Find this ciego and kill him.

272
00:26:30,288 --> 00:26:31,813
I will kill the blind man!

273
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:39,221
Be sure to gouge out his eyes
and bring them to me.

274
00:26:45,470 --> 00:26:48,804
We are going to see who is blind.

275
00:26:54,279 --> 00:26:56,008
It's just too much.

276
00:27:12,564 --> 00:27:13,622
That's it.

277
00:27:14,132 --> 00:27:15,497
200 pounds.

278
00:27:16,001 --> 00:27:17,992
Did you forget something?

279
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,162
Yeah.

280
00:27:25,410 --> 00:27:29,210
They say these are rolled on the thighs
of a Cuban virgin.

281
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:34,651
- I believe them.
- I find it highly unlikely.

282
00:27:34,753 --> 00:27:37,552
Hell, a man's got to dream.

283
00:27:38,056 --> 00:27:40,388
- Take that to my room...
- That's not the deal.

284
00:27:40,458 --> 00:27:42,859
It stays here until
you bring reinforcements.

285
00:27:42,927 --> 00:27:44,292
Fine.

286
00:27:45,897 --> 00:27:47,365
But not here.

287
00:28:00,378 --> 00:28:01,504
Canaan!

288
00:28:04,149 --> 00:28:06,117
What do I tell them when I'm short?

289
00:28:06,184 --> 00:28:10,951
You can say it fell off the wagon while
you boys were out there running yellow.

290
00:28:18,496 --> 00:28:20,021
Son of a bitch.

291
00:29:00,505 --> 00:29:01,939
That's enough!

292
00:29:04,109 --> 00:29:07,374
How dare you defile the house of God!

293
00:29:07,946 --> 00:29:09,675
I told you to get...

294
