315
00:31:07,765 --> 00:31:10,530
I'll take that under consideration.

316
00:31:15,273 --> 00:31:19,471
You should lie down. You need at least
a day's rest before you leave.

317
00:31:19,544 --> 00:31:20,909
I'm leaving tonight.

318
00:31:20,979 --> 00:31:23,004
That's not advisable.

319
00:31:23,548 --> 00:31:25,516
Are these doctor's orders?

320
00:31:28,319 --> 00:31:31,186
Yes, they're doctor's orders.

321
00:31:31,789 --> 00:31:33,518
I'll tell you what.

322
00:31:35,293 --> 00:31:37,785
I'll take that under consideration.

323
00:31:56,247 --> 00:31:57,874
What's your name?

324
00:31:58,583 --> 00:32:01,348
Fowler, Ernie Fowler.

325
00:32:03,521 --> 00:32:06,354
You can call me Ernie,
everybody else does.

326
00:32:07,892 --> 00:32:10,691
Does this place look as bad as it smells?

327
00:32:11,329 --> 00:32:12,558
Hell, no!

328
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:20,235
