329
00:32:22,407 --> 00:32:25,399
- Pretty as a San Francisco whorehouse.
- Crystal chandeliers?

330
00:32:25,510 --> 00:32:29,970
Hell, yes! Got me a solid marble bar
right there to belly up to.

331
00:32:30,782 --> 00:32:34,082
That there, it's Italian marble.

332
00:32:34,152 --> 00:32:36,780
